k\">https://t.me/joinchat/H9HhP1GjqX7E0kHgLmf8xw</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">[size=6]其他紀律部隊戰線:</span></div><br />\n拉攏非警察的紀律部隊，要求表態，為違反紀律部隊職責的警察投訴<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[gold]721宣言</span></span><br />\n<br />\n    <br />\n    <a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTey%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=c976e356\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n條片只有[green]3000views<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>TG香港本土化<br />\n</strong></span></div><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/localization_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flocalization_hk&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTey%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=95b9d792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/localization_hk</a><br />\n香港話<br />\ntg://setlanguage?lang=hongkonger<br />\n適用於：Android／iOS<br />\n<br />\n廣東話<br />\ntg://setlanguage?lang=cantonese<br />\n適用於：Android／iOS／TDesktop<br />\n<br />\n港式潮語<br />\ntg://setlanguage?lang=hkslang<br />\n適用於：Android／iOS<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">歡迎轉發及引用推Post</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"18bd268c86c7c8030ee8f28f756a9b8ca6ef3089","tid":1359234,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f45d3f2819dbc33995e2e74a244d69142e708ee","tid":1359234,"uid":160247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill